node.text: It’s been a minute but we’re back!  2022! 😈 #StrangerThings #Season4 #ST4

node.text: I saw this quote the other day, “You don’t only live once, you live everyday.” So this a reminder to take advantage of YOUR time and go after what you want in YOUR life. Find YOUR happiness, don’t do it for other people do it for YOURSELF! People will always judge and have an opinion about YOU or what they think they know about YOU. You can’t allow people to dictate YOUR happiness because you will regret that you allowed them to stay in your head rent free. I LOVE YOU ALL GENUINELY ❤️❤️❤️ #BeYourBiggestFan#EmbraceYourFace
